        "captions": "[{\"start\": 0, \"end\": 8448000, \"text\": \"出国买错东西退换不用慌！\\n收藏这 5 句，覆盖从说明诉求到确认退款的全流程表达\\n1. I'd like to return this shirt.\\n2. It's too small for me.\\n3. Do you have a larger size?\\n4. When will the refund come through?\\n5. Can I get a new bag for this?\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 8448000, \"end\": 13680000, \"text\": \"I'd like to return this shirt.\\n我想退这件衬衫\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 13680000, \"end\": 18504000, \"text\": \"It's too small for me.\\n它对我来说太小了\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 18504000, \"end\": 23328000, \"text\": \"Do you have a larger size?\\n你们有更大码的吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 23328000, \"end\": 29376000, \"text\": \"When will the refund come through?\\n退款什么时候到账？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 29376000, \"end\": 35016000, \"text\": \"Can I get a new bag for this?\\n能给我个新袋子装这个吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 35016000, \"end\": 39048000, \"text\": \"你出国旅游有没有遇到过要退换货的情况呀？\", \"font_size\": 10}]",
